| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4766 — Recovery Inhibition (dispossessor)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a18e2949-37b0-5d31-920f-b4e7596a3aaa"
